<h1>layered-managed-resource-rails (v<%= Layered::ManagedResource::VERSION %>)</h1>

<p class="l-ui-utility--mt-md">
  <%= Gem.loaded_specs["layered-managed-resource-rails"].description %>
</p>

<h2 class="l-ui-utility--mt-xl">Demo</h2>
<ul class="l-ui-list l-ui-utility--mt-md">
  <li><%= link_to "Posts (full CRUD)", managed_posts_path %> — index, new, create, edit, update, destroy</li>
  <li><%= link_to "Readonly", managed_readonly_posts_path %> — index only</li>
  <li><%= link_to "Deletable", managed_deletable_posts_path %> — index and destroy</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="l-ui-utility--mt-xl">Requirements</h2>
<ul class="l-ui-list l-ui-utility--mt-md">
  <li>Ruby on Rails >= 8.0</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/layered-ai-public/layered-ui-rails">layered-ui-rails</a> ~> 0.3</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/activerecord-hackery/ransack">Ransack</a> ~> 4.0</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/ddnexus/pagy">Pagy</a> ~> 43.2</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="l-ui-utility--mt-xl">Installation</h2>
<p class="l-ui-utility--mt-md">Add to your Gemfile:</p>
<pre class="l-ui-surface l-ui-utility--mt-md"><code>gem "layered-managed-resource-rails"</code></pre>
<p class="l-ui-utility--mt-lg">Then run:</p>
<pre class="l-ui-surface l-ui-utility--mt-md"><code>bundle install</code></pre>

<h2 class="l-ui-utility--mt-xl">Setup</h2>

<h3 class="l-ui-utility--mt-lg">1. Routes</h3>
<p class="l-ui-utility--mt-md">Use <code>l_managed_resources</code> in your routes to register a model for CRUD management:</p>
<pre class="l-ui-surface l-ui-utility--mt-md"><code># config/routes.rb
l_managed_resources :posts</code></pre>
<p class="l-ui-utility--mt-md">Restrict actions with the <code>only:</code> option:</p>
<pre class="l-ui-surface l-ui-utility--mt-md"><code>l_managed_resources :posts, only: [:index]            # read-only
l_managed_resources :posts, only: %i[index destroy]    # list + delete</code></pre>

<h3 class="l-ui-utility--mt-lg">2. Model</h3>
<p class="l-ui-utility--mt-md">Include <code>Layered::ManagedResource::Resource</code> in your model and configure the interface:</p>
<pre class="l-ui-surface l-ui-utility--mt-md"><code>class Post < ApplicationRecord
  include Layered::ManagedResource::Resource

  def self.l_managed_resource_columns
    [
      { attribute: :title, primary: true },
      { attribute: :created_at, label: "Created" }
    ]
  end

  def self.l_managed_resource_fields
    [
      { attribute: :title, required: true },
      { attribute: :body, as: :text }
    ]
  end

  def self.l_managed_resource_search_fields
    [:title, :body]
  end
end</code></pre>

<h3 class="l-ui-utility--mt-lg">3. Model configuration</h3>
<p class="l-ui-utility--mt-md">Override these class methods to customise behaviour:</p>
<% config_methods = [
  { method: "l_managed_resource_columns", purpose: "Columns displayed on the index table" },
  { method: "l_managed_resource_fields", purpose: "Form fields for new/edit (empty = read-only, no CRUD forms)" },
  { method: "l_managed_resource_search_fields", purpose: "Ransack search attributes" },
  { method: "l_managed_resource_default_sort", purpose: "Default sort order for the index" },
  { method: "l_managed_resource_permitted_params", purpose: "Strong params (derived from fields by default)" },
  { method: "l_managed_resource_scope(controller)", purpose: "Base scope (override for tenant isolation)" },
  { method: "l_managed_resource_build_record(controller)", purpose: "How to instantiate new records" },
  { method: "l_managed_resource_after_save_path(controller, record)", purpose: "Redirect target after create/update/destroy" }
] %>

<div class="l-ui-utility--mt-md">
  <%= l_ui_table(config_methods,
        columns: [
          { attribute: :method, label: "Method", render: ->(r) { tag.code(r[:method]) } },
          { attribute: :purpose, label: "Purpose" }
        ],
        caption: "Model configuration methods") %>
</div>

<h2 class="l-ui-utility--mt-xl">Authentication</h2>
<p class="l-ui-utility--mt-md">Protect managed resources with a before_action by setting:</p>
<pre class="l-ui-surface l-ui-utility--mt-md"><code># config/initializers/managed_resource.rb
Layered::ManagedResource.l_managed_resource_before_action = :authenticate_user!</code></pre>

